<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Página no encontrada | Lotería Manises</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #1f2937;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .not-found-container {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: clamp(2.25rem, 2vw + 1.5rem, 3rem) 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }

    .not-found-title {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.25rem;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .not-found-title .highlight {
      color: #004394;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 2.8vw + 1rem, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      line-height: 1.05;
    }

    .not-found-title .subtitle {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1vw + 0.8rem, 1.4rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      max-width: 780px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .not-found-image {
      max-width: 1000px;
      width: min(92vw, 1000px);
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: block;
    }

    .not-found-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #004394;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .not-found-button:hover {
      background-color: #0b4792;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .not-found-button:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .not-found-text {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      max-width: 640px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .not-found-container {
        padding: 2.25rem 1.25rem;
      }

      .not-found-title {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .not-found-image {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .not-found-container {
        max-width: 95vw;
      }

      .not-found-title .highlight {
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw + 0.9rem, 2.8rem);
      }

      .not-found-title .subtitle {
        font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.2vw + 0.75rem, 1.25rem);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .not-found-container {
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      .not-found-title {
        gap: 0.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }

      .not-found-title .subtitle {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .not-found-image {
        max-width: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }

      .not-found-button {
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        min-width: min(88vw, 320px);
      }

      .not-found-text {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .not-found-container {
        padding: 1.75rem 1rem;
      }

      .not-found-title .highlight {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .not-found-title .subtitle {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }

      .not-found-button {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="not-found-container">
    <h1 class="not-found-title">
      <span class="highlight">¡Ups!</span>
      <span class="subtitle">Esta página se nos ha escapado del bombo y&nbsp;seguimos&nbsp;buscándola!</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Usando ruta relativa para que funcione al abrir el HTML localmente -->
    <img src="/Web_2_0/Pagina en mantenimiento/images/maqueta_404_h.jpg" alt="Error 404 - Página no encontrada" class="not-found-image" />

    <a href="https://www.loteriamanises.com/" class="not-found-button">
      Volver al inicio
    </a>

    <p class="not-found-text">
      La página que buscas no está disponible, o quizás... ¡está esperando ser descubierta en otro sorteo!
    </p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>